Let n number.
Let result be number.

Get number ask "Enter a number:" storeInto n.

To factorial with x:
    Let i be number.
    Let r be number.
    Set i to 1 times 5 plus 2.
    Set r to 1.
    While i atMost x:
        Multiply r by i.
        Increase i by 1.
    Return r.

Set result to factorial with (n).

Show "The factorial is:".
Show result.